    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document describes the requirements for the logical entity known as the Session Initiation Protocol (SIP)-H.323 Interworking Function (SIP-H.323 IWF) that will allow the interworking between SIP and H.323.  This memo provides information for the Internet community.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
